    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >背景介绍</h2><strong>建安十三年，曹操兵败赤壁损失惨重，此战尔后便奠定了三国鼎立的雏型。为抵御孙刘联军，曹操下令帐下发丘将军与摸金校尉秘密前往探寻传说中的“长生不老药”及可召千万阴兵的“鬼玺”。此二人风餐露宿耗时数年历经千辛万苦方才在一座深山老林中寻到一座千年古墓，在二人商讨下，决定由摸金校尉折返将此事禀告曹操，而发丘中郎将一人下墓寻宝......</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主线模式</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>收集场景中的物品和线索<br></li><li>破解机关继续前进<br></li><li>击败你看到的敌人汲取他们的灵魂</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1843290/extras/8294d36bbcbf1650e0254f01141b7ff5.poster.avif?t=1641732610\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1843290/extras/8294d36bbcbf1650e0254f01141b7ff5.webm?t=1641732610\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1843290/extras/8294d36bbcbf1650e0254f01141b7ff5.mp4?t=1641732610\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1843290/extras/931861488ad63848a9168add2555d5c9.poster.avif?t=1641732610\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1843290/extras/931861488ad63848a9168add2555d5c9.webm?t=1641732610\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1843290/extras/931861488ad63848a9168add2555d5c9.mp4?t=1641732610\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >遁入幻境</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>区别于主线地图，使用独立的地图。<br></li><li>挑战任何的BOSS，获取大量的灵魂。<br></li><li>不断挑战自我，使用最少的时间击败敌人！</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1843290/extras/97ffa5207aa3b08b65bc0715ca97d9ae.poster.avif?t=1641732610\" width=620 height=348 ><